#: includes/Admin/Test_Page.php:840
msgid "Scope"
msgstr "Alcance"

#: includes/Admin/Test_Page.php:841
msgid ""
"These checks run registered read-only abilities with bounded admin input. "
"They do not write content, call models, or contact external services; the "
"diagnostics check omits plugin rows, current-user details, updates, and cron "
"details."
msgstr ""
"Estas comprobaciones ejecutan capacidades de solo lectura con entrada "
"administrativa acotada. No escriben contenido, no llaman a modelos ni "
"contactan servicios externos; el diagnóstico omite filas de plugins, "
"detalles del usuario actual, actualizaciones y detalles de cron."

